query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(c l o s d) */ select c.c_city,
s.s_city,
d.d_year,
sum(l.l_revenue) AS revenue
from supplier AS s
inner join lineitem AS l
on l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND s.s_nation = 'UNITED STATES'
inner join orders AS o
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
inner join customer AS c
on o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND c.c_nation = 'UNITED STATES'
inner join date AS d
on o.o_orderdate = d.d_datekey AND d.d_year >= 1992 AND d.d_year <= 1997 group by c.c_city, s.s_city, d.d_year order by d.d_year asc, revenue desc;
